## Supported Canvases

### 1. Business Model Canvas (BMC)
9 building blocks:
- Customer Segments
- Value Propositions
- Channels
- Customer Relationships
- Revenue Streams
- Key Resources
- Key Activities
- Key Partnerships
- Cost Structure

### 2. Lean Canvas
Startup-focused adaptation:
- Problem (top 3 problems)
- Solution (top 3 features)
- Key Metrics
- Unique Value Proposition
- Unfair Advantage
- Channels
- Customer Segments
- Cost Structure
- Revenue Streams

### 3. Value Proposition Canvas
Deep customer fit:
- **Customer Profile:**
  - Jobs to be done
  - Pains
  - Gains
- **Value Map:**
  - Products & Services
  - Pain Relievers
  - Gain Creators

## Key Components

- **Canvas grid** - 9-block responsive layout
- **Sticky notes** - Items within each block
- **Color coding** - Category differentiation
- **Fit indicators** - Value prop alignment

